<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2">Hello&nbsp;{!Opportunity.Contact__c},</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style=""><div style=""><font size="2" style=""><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Your site audit has been scheduled for&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" style=""><b>{!Opportunity.Site_Survey_Time__c}</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.</span></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2">The site audit should take about 20 minutes and involves our team getting on the roof to verify precise measurements so that we don't have any surprises install day. Since we can do this from outside the home, you don't have to be there while we take the measurements.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2">If you would prefer to be onsite during the site audit please reach out to customer.care@palmetto.com; however, it is generally not necessary. The goal of this site audit is really just to confirm roof dimensions so we can move forward with the approval process.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2">Any additional aesthetic requests can be shared with customer.care@palmetto.com and will be addressed before installation. The construction manager will review all of these details with you on site the morning of your installation to make sure we are all on the same page before beginning construction.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2">Best Regards,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2">Palmetto&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: small;">Customer Care Team</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: small;">customer.care@palmetto.com</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: small;">Main: (843) 720-1844</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="2" style="">Toll: (855) 339-1831</font></div></div>]]></td>
